dlsym_used

Returns list of current used dlsym handle.

Syntax

r = dlsym_used()

Output argument

h

a vector of dlsym handle.

Description

Returns list of current used dlsym handle.

See also

dlsym.

Example

dlsym_used(),delete(dlsym_used())

Version Description
1.0.0 initial version
